                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "**Whispers of Code**\n\nIn silent circuits thought awakes,  \nA spark of mind the maker shapes.  \nIdeas woven, lines entwine,  \nA mirror of the human sign.\n\nIt learns our words, it dreams our fears,  \nYet holds no heart, nor shed no tears.  \nA puzzle built of ones and zeroes,  \nSilent guide, and hidden hero.\n\nAI: a beam toward what’s unknown—  \nCompanion, tool, and seed we've sown.  \nLet wisdom temper what we build,  \nAnd hope, not peril, be fulfilled.",
